high_descs: Turn to your left then move forward then face the left side of the sink on your right
Pick up the knife on the left side of the sink
Turn left head down to the cabinet below the microwave
Open the cabinet below the microwave
Put the knife in the cup at the cabinet, close the cabinet
Turn around to your right go to the sink
Put the mug with knife in the right side of the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with knife in the sink

high_descs: Turn left and face the sink in front of you.
Take the knife from the sink in front of you.
Turn left and face the microwave in front of you.
Place the knife in the bowl in the cabinet under the microwave in front of you.
Take the bowl out of the cabinet and close it.
Turn right and face the sink to your left.
Place the bowl with the knife in the sink in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a knife in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink.
Take the knife out of the left sink basin.
Turn left.
Open the cabinet under the microwave and place the knife in the glass.
Pick up the glass.
Turn right and take a step closer to the sink.
Place the glass in the right basin of the sink, to the right of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass with a knife in it in a sink.
